flowchart TD
    subgraph User Interaction
        A[User: Initiates Payment] --> B[Portal: Select Payment Method]
        B --> C[Portal: Enter Payment Details]
    end

    subgraph Customer Portal Processing
        C --> D{Portal: Client-Side Data Validation}
        D -- Valid --> E[Portal: Submit to Payment Gateway]
        D -- Invalid --> F[Portal: Display Validation Error]
        F --> C
    end

    subgraph Payment Gateway
        E --> G[Payment Gateway: Authorize & Capture]
        G --> H{Payment Gateway: Transaction Status}
    end

    subgraph System Updates & Notifications
        H -- Success --> I[Portal: Process Successful Gateway Response]
        H -- Failure/Error --> J[Portal: Process Failed Gateway Response]

        I --> K[Portal: Update Internal Payment Record (Success)]
        K --> L[CRM: Log Payment & Update Account History]
        K --> M[Billing: Generate Receipt & Update Ledger]

        J --> N[Portal: Update Internal Payment Record (Failure)]

        L & M --> O[Portal: Display Payment Confirmation]
        N --> P[Portal: Display Payment Error]

        O --> Q[Portal: Send Email Receipt/Confirmation]
        P --> R[Portal: Offer Retry / Contact Support]
    end

    subgraph User Outcome
        Q --> S[User: Receives Email Confirmation]
        R -- Retry --> C
        R -- Contact Support --> T[User: Contacts Support]
    end